0.130 0.150 0.190 rg BT /F1 11.20 Tf 66.00 330.26 Td (3. `values.yaml` defines a default image, replica count, and service port.) Tj ET
0.130 0.150 0.190 rg BT /F1 11.20 Tf 66.00 311.46 Td (4. The production team provides a separate values file with higher replicas and a) Tj ET
0.130 0.150 0.190 rg BT /F1 11.20 Tf 82.00 294.66 Td (production domain.) Tj ET
