0.130 0.150 0.190 rg BT /F1 11.20 Tf 66.00 238.26 Td (7. Kubernetes creates or updates the resources.) Tj ET
0.130 0.150 0.190 rg BT /F1 11.20 Tf 66.00 219.46 Td (8. Helm records the release revision so the team can upgrade or roll back later.) Tj ET
